    1833 EQUIVX Data block name equivalence Main Index Attaches a second name to an existing data block.     EQUIVX Data block name equivalence1834 Main Index 4.If DBS is also declared on the FILE DBS=APPEND statement then User Warning Message 81 will be issued. However, if the EQUIVX statement is potentially re-executed then it should be replaced with the DELETE and COPY module.
